        </title>
        <p id="Par24"><italic>(Compatibility</italic> [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR10">10</xref>]<italic>)</italic> A set of unordered splits <inline-formula id="IEq26"><alternatives><tex-math id="M51">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
