        <p>We will make use of the implied one to one correspondence of edges in a tree and compatible splits: an edge of length <italic>w</italic> whose removal separates a tree into two trees with leaf sets <italic>A</italic> and <italic>B</italic>, respectively, corresponds to a split <inline-formula id="IEq33"><alternatives><tex-math id="M65">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
