				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$(k\!-\!2)$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M252"><mml:mrow><mml:mo stretchy="false">(</mml:mo><mml:mi>k</mml:mi><mml:mspace width="-0.166667em"/><mml:mo>-</mml:mo><mml:mspace width="-0.166667em"/><mml:mn>2</mml:mn><mml:mo stretchy="false">)</mml:mo></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13015_2020_164_Article_IEq79.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>-mer counts by subtracting random background of neutral mutations using a <inline-formula id="IEq80"><alternatives><tex-math id="M253">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
